OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FAfter yesterday's PMQs, as MPs hurried
OL,8,Fout of the chamber, Labour MPs made
OL,9,Ftheir way to the Wilson Room, a large
OL,10,Fmeeting space on the parliamentary
OL,11,Festate, for a briefing on welfare
OL,12,Freforms led by Liz Kendall, the Shadow
OL,13,FWork and Pensions Secretary.
OL,15,FThe meeting, described by one attendee
OL,16,Fas "highly unusual," drew more than
OL,17,F100 Labour MPs, as Kendall attempted
OL,18,Fto reassure colleagues concerned about
OL,19,Fthe proposed cuts.
