OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FMPs from across the party's
OL,8,Fideological spectrum were present,
OL,9,Fwith the most pressing questions
OL,10,Ffocused on changes to PIP eligibility
OL,11,Fand the impact on young people in
OL,12,Fparticular, with one source in the
OL,13,Froom describing the atmosphere as
OL,14,F"incredibly tense".
