OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FOne left-leaning Labour MP
OL,8,Facknowledged that some reform was
OL,9,Fnecessary but said the scale of the
OL,10,Fcuts, and the suggestion that raising
OL,11,Fconcerns meant "defending a rotten
OL,12,Fwelfare system", had left many deeply
OL,13,Funeasy.
OL,15,FAnother MP noted that most attendees
OL,16,Fwalked away feeling worse than when
OL,17,Fthey arrived.
