OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FThe changes include tightening the
OL,8,Feligibility criteria for disability
OL,9,Fbenefits, scrapping a controversial
OL,10,Fbenefits assessment, and raising the
OL,11,Fbasic rate of universal credit while
OL,12,Fcutting the higher rate for those too
OL,13,Fill to work.
OL,15,F"Millions of people who could work
OL,16,F(are) trapped on benefits," Kendall
OL,17,Ftold MPs in the House of Commons on
OL,18,FTuesday, insisting the current welfare
OL,19,Fsystem is "holding the country back".
