OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FITV News Deputy Political Editor
OL,8,FAnushka Asthana revealed details of
OL,9,Fthe cuts just over a week ago,
OL,10,Fsparking a fierce backlash from Labour
OL,11,FMPs and causing the government to
OL,12,Frethink some of the measures.
OL,14,FSir Keir Starmer is targeting benefits
OL,15,Fbecause the bill has rocketed in
OL,16,Frecent years, reaching #48 billion
OL,17,Flast year.
