OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FThe number of people in England and
OL,8,FWales claiming either sickness or
OL,9,Fdisability benefit has risen sharply
OL,10,Ffrom 2.8 million in 2019 to around
OL,11,Ffour million today.
OL,13,F"The reason we are doing this is
OL,14,Fbecause we do not believe the current
OL,15,Fsystem is working for the people who
OL,16,Fdepend on it, and it's not working for
OL,17,Ftaxpayers either," Kendall told
OL,18,FAnushka Asthana.
