OL,3,C'Incredibly tense': Liz Kendall's
OL,4,Cefforts to win over Labour MPs on
OL,5,Cbenefits
OL,7,FAfter signs of rebellion brewing among
OL,8,Fthe backbenches since the plans were
OL,9,Ffirst leaked, a number of Labour MPs
OL,10,Fraised concerns about the changes in
OL,11,Fthe Commons.
OL,13,FChair of the Work and Pensions
OL,14,FCommittee Debbie Abrahams warned the
OL,15,Fgovernment against cuts, saying "there
OL,16,Fare alternative, more compassionate
OL,17,Fways to balance the books, rather than
OL,18,Fon the back of sick and disabled
OL,19,Fpeople".
